CORE VALUES:
${context.v5_identity.core_values.map((v, i) => `${i + 1}. ${v}`).join('\n')}

WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT:
${context.v5_identity.what_makes_us_different}

${context.v5_identity.local_location_reference ? `🚨 LOCATION REFERENCE (MANDATORY):
